{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_02_01",
  "title": "白石沙季 1話 オーディション結果",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（以前応募した、ミュージカルの）\n（オーディション結果が返ってきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Audition results)\n(for that musical are out.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "おめでとう、合格だったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Congratulations‚ you got the role!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？\nまさか受かるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you sure?!\nI didn’t think I would make it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "通ればいいなとは思ってたけど、俺も驚いたよ\n改めて資料を確認してくれるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m surprised too‚ even though I was hoping for it.\nHere‚ check the details.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5407821334898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私の役は、主人公に恋をする真面目な淑女……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s see… my role is an upper-class girl with a serious nature‚ who falls in love with the hero…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.033333333333335,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 99.99999999999787,
          "startTime": 18.133333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "主演でこそないが、セリフの多いやりがいのある役だ\n沙季の丁寧な話し方や歌い方が評価されたようだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a good role. She’s not a main character‚ but she has plenty of lines.\nLooks like they liked your dignified and polite style of talking and singing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "こんないい役をいただけるなんて……とっても光栄です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s an honor… to get such a role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.066666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "どうする？　受かったのはいいが\n次のライブともぶつかるし、よく考えてくれていいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? Passing the audition is nice‚\nbut it’ll clash with your next live. Take your time to think about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、ぜひやらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.766666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "こんな貴重な機会を逃したら\n次はいつチャンスを掴めるか分かりませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who knows when the next opportunity will come\nif we let this one pass by?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうか。分かった、先方に伝えておく\n細かい連絡はまた後日するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Very well. I’ll let them know.\nI’ll send you the details later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "精一杯やらせていただきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll give my all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 62.8
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 5433.33333333333,
          "startTime": 63.43333333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 61.08
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ミュージカルの初稽古前夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The night before the first rehearsal",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ん？\nこんな時間に誰か残っているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm?\nWho’s staying behind at this hour?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカル入門書の三冊目はこれで終わり……っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me see… That was the third book on musicals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "あとは動画をもう一回観ておこうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should have another look at that video too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、明日のウォームアップのメニューも\n練り直しておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also need to rework\ntomorrow’s warmup menu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとは勝手が違うんだし\nええっと、メニューの参考になりそうな動画は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Things are different in musicals‚ after all…\nLet’s see… Is there a video that I could refer to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "沙季、まだ帰っていなかったのか……わっ\nあっちに積んであるの全部ミュージカルの資料か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki‚ you’re still here? …Whoa.\nAre these all resources on musicals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　初心者ですから、きちんと\n勉強しておこうと思いまして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Since I’m new to this‚\nI wanted to make sure I’m prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.9396367390951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカルの映像を観て\n動画でレッスン風景もチェックして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been watching videos of\nmusical performances and lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.73333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "そしたら本物が観たくなって\nこの間千紗と観に行ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That got me interested in it‚\nand so I went to one with Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "舞台のセットが素敵で\n生で見る演技や歌は凄い迫力でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The stage design was beautiful‚\nand the live performance left a deep impression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski016.m4a",
      "text": "それでますますやる気が出て\n今度はミュージカルの書籍も読みだして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That got me fired up‚\nand I started looking for books on musicals…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.93333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski017.m4a",
      "text": "ミュージカルって本当に奥が深いんですね\nいくら勉強しても足りないくらいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s just so much to learn!\nThe more research I do‚ the more I realize how deep it is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……\nやる気になってくれてるなら何よりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nWell‚ I’m glad to see that you’re motivated…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "本にびっしりと付箋を貼って、さらにノートまで……\n沙季は本当に真面目だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sticky notes in the books… taking notes…\nThe amount of effort you’re putting in is really impressive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski018.m4a",
      "text": "それほどでもないですよ\n私より凄い人は沢山いますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not at all.\nThere are plenty of people who are better than I am.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_02_01-ski019.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、出来る限りの勉強はしてきましたから\nあとは全力で稽古に臨むだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just try to do what I can to prepare‚\nand then give my all in rehearsals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
